{"tid":2406480,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"市民捐款抗打壓 支聯會籌得50萬","createTime":"2021-02-13T08:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T16:16:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9eb2549200b67010495576115b59ba918f84f6f6","tid":2406480,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:30:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210213/ZZTPUPZH7JDDRJXWD2SSZ7EBYI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210213%2FZZTPUPZH7JDDRJXWD2SSZ7EBYI%2F&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=0f961851\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210213%2FZZTPUPZH7JDDRJXWD2SSZ7EBYI%2F&h=b043bac4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210213/ZZTPUPZH7JDDRJXWD2SSZ7EBYI/</a><br />\n<br />\n市民捐款抗打壓 支聯會籌得50萬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/c3ZOKVPLXipwZGJHEMYYBJHHfVw=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AFRXTTUPDBDHPCFVAFSJXKJA6A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fc3ZOKVPLXipwZGJHEMYYBJHHfVw%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAFRXTTUPDBDHPCFVAFSJXKJA6A.jpg&h=ee038148&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■食環以攤位內容與賣花無關為由，先要求支聯會拆除，最終突襲封檔。<br />\n<br />\n後來我們都知道，今年維園年宵再無支聯會蹤影。年宵開鑼前兩天，工作人員仍頂着太陽，努力搭起19號和20號攤檔，準備掛上31年屹立未倒的「平反六四」、「建設民主中國、建設民主香港」橫額，一切如火如荼&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：無懼波折 深信仍是會開花<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/S02oe51iOVg6edkWoQLfds5EAaE=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4STWFX6NS5GBNLSZER5DB5PQR4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FS02oe51iOVg6edkWoQLfds5EAaE%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4STWFX6NS5GBNLSZER5DB5PQR4.jpg&h=997b0117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■年宵開鑼前，蔡耀昌已坦言只能抱「最後一次」心態參與。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「𠵱家每做一樣嘢，都要諗今次會唔會就係最後一次。」<br />\n<br />\n「今年32周年主題係『為自由 共命運 同抗爭』。」攤檔未被禁前，支聯會秘書蔡耀昌站在棚架前介紹花種。<br />\n<br />\n2月4日，記者在攤檔前問蔡耀昌，有否想過今年或是最後一年支聯會維園年宵？他哽咽說：「香港人今日都唔知聽日點，支聯會都唔知能唔能夠捱過今年&hellip;&hellip;𠵱家每做一樣嘢，都要諗今次會唔會就係最後一次。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：蘭花大王收拾心情 為來年苦幹<br />\n<br />\n翌日，食環到支聯會攤檔張貼警告信，指攤位內容與賣花無關，要求兩小時內拆除，支聯會以紙張和布遮蓋部份字眼。6日凌晨，食環再突襲張貼終止合約通知書，要求早上7時將物資搬走。<br />\n<br />\n維園年宵年廿五早上9時開鑼，支聯會攤檔營業僅20分鐘，食環、保安架起鐵馬封檔。支聯會成員只能清場離開，蔡耀昌說，打壓來得比他想像中早和粗暴。<br />\n<br />\n五萬元成本，頓時血本無歸。惟一方有難，八方支援：支聯會常委、葵青區區議員梁錦威把上千盆栽送予葵青區議員和街坊；灣仔區議會主席楊雪瑩把運花至大坑，呼籲公眾捐款支持支聯會六四集會案的訟費。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會失去維園年宵，但力保港人支持。截至年初一中午12時，支聯會共籌得48萬港元，共592次入賬，平均每次入賬超過800元。捐款包括尊子網上義畫400張肖像籌款，共收捐款近16萬元。<br />\n<br />\n蔡耀昌認為籌款比想像中更理想，「顯示香港人對公義嘅追求，對支聯會同抗爭活動嘅支持。」但他遺憾無法參與年宵，「我哋都想接觸市民，宣傳理念」。"},{"pid":"f16962c979c05776d824ab55784f2138309dd942","tid":2406480,"uid":292362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9eb2549200b67010495576115b59ba918f84f6f6","tid":2406480,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T08:30:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210213/ZZTPUPZH7JDDRJXWD2SSZ7EBYI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210213%2FZZTPUPZH7JDDRJXWD2SSZ7EBYI%2F&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=0f961851\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210213%2FZZTPUPZH7JDDRJXWD2SSZ7EBYI%2F&h=b043bac4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210213/ZZTPUPZH7JDDRJXWD2SSZ7EBYI/</a><br />\n<br />\n市民捐款抗打壓 支聯會籌得50萬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/c3ZOKVPLXipwZGJHEMYYBJHHfVw=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AFRXTTUPDBDHPCFVAFSJXKJA6A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t